@startuml
title SE DuKhach DangKy
actor "Du khách" as U
participant "TouristRegisterPage.OnRegisterClicked()" as UI
participant "TouristAuthService.RegisterAsync()" as SVC
participant "TravelGuide.API Program.cs MapPost(\"/api/tourist/auth/register\")" as API
database "TravelGuide.API.Data.TouristDb.CreateUserAsync(username, password, displayName, tier)" as DB
U -> UI : Bấm đăng ký
UI -> UI : Kiểm tra độ dài username/displayName/password (trong OnRegisterClicked)
UI -> SVC : RegisterAsync(username, password, displayName, accountTier)
SVC -> API : POST /api/tourist/auth/register
API -> API : TouristDb.NormalizeUsername / NormalizeAccountTier
API -> DB : CreateUserAsync(...)
DB --> API : bool created
API --> SVC : 200/400 + message
SVC --> UI : (Ok, Message)
UI --> UI : DisplayAlert + Shell khi thành công
@enduml
